OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 03 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1968FTWW ceased broadcasting. The
OL,7,Fstation lost its franchise in the
OL,8,Fprevious ITV licensing awards and
OL,9,Fdecided to close 10 weeks early. It
OL,10,Fsold its remaining airtime to HTV for
OL,11,F#500,000. However Harlech was not ready
OL,12,Fto commence transmissions. To fill the
OL,13,Fgap, an interim service, staffed by
OL,14,Fformer TWW staff, was provided until
OL,15,FHarlech's launch on Monday 20th May
OL,16,F1968.
